#

Classic Fish and Chips

35 min
$15
800 kcal
Difficulty: 25%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

FishGluten

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinLow Carb

Cuisine:

British

Course:

Main Course

Tags:

Comfort FoodQuick MealBritish Cuisine

Description

Crispy battered fish served with golden fries, a classic British delight that’s easy to enjoy!

Ingredients

  • cod fillets: 2 pieces
  • potatoes: 2 large
  • all-purpose flour: 1 cup
  • cornstarch: 1/4 cup
  • baking powder: 1 teaspoon
  • cold sparkling water: 1 cup
  • vegetable oil: for frying
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • paprika: 1 teaspoon
  • tartar sauce: for serving
  • lemon wedges: for serving
